==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: zìzú 

===Adjective===
'''[[自足]]'''

# ([[沾沾自喜]]) to feel complacent over sth.; to feel smug; to be pleased with oneself; to congratulate oneself; to hug oneself
# self-satisfied; self-congratulatory; complacent; smug
#: ''[[道理]][[无穷]]，[[学者]][[先]][[要不得]][[有]]'''自足'''[[心]]'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''[[道理]][[無窮]]，[[學者]][[先]][[要不得]][[有]]'''自足'''[[心]]'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: Truth is infinite; a scholar can not afford to have a '''complacent''' attitude.''
# ([[自給自足]], [[自给自足]]) self-sufficient

